{"tid":802660,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Graphic designer想轉做UI designer應該由邊到學起？","createTime":"2018-09-01T15:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T06:58:46.000Z","uid":127439,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"320948da0b0e98816f861ef4578dc1af7d40a6d3","tid":802660,"uid":127439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"做緊in-house graphic design<br />\n自己一直都有啲心思思想做ui design<br />\n加上最近有個機會可以做responsive website ui<br />\n不過需要做埋部份ux野<br />\n自覺對於ux需要既邏輯性思考唔係好夠<br />\n不過見有機會咁咪試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但發覺自己連做ui點開波做都唔識<br />\n上網google見好似有好多方法<br />\n由畫wireframe, prototype咁開始<br />\nSoftware就用sketch<br />\n不過因為真係第一次接觸ui design唔知個正確workflow係點？<br />\n連畫個wireframe都唔知應該點開始<br />\n我知自己好撚癈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求有經驗巴絲指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實見出面市場趨勢都對ui/ux有需求<br />\n一直都想話take返啲ui相關course<br />\n繼而轉做ui designer(因為人工至少好過淨係識graphic<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n但香港又唔多呢類既course, 一係就係得啲19私人學院開既19 course，台灣線上都有啲但係教software既多, 除左software既技術我想學返啲深入少少既野<br />\n<br />\n有冇做開呢行既巴絲可以比下意見指教指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉行短期黎講都唔會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都想試下做ui/ux先<br />\n因為除左設計我真係乜撚都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5662f425f5fe25bacedb6b77588d7803282260","tid":802660,"uid":4531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea0659815fac065aa4c1af905b4db09ae6829ce5","tid":802660,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f5662f425f5fe